12:36.990 --> 12:38.725 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

12:38.758 --> 12:40.860 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN MCCAIN (R), Arizona: What's
