20:06.972 --> 20:08.140 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: Right.

20:08.174 --> 20:08.974 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: And then what
