20:17.850 --> 20:20.686 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to do, and then eventually
denied the permit
for it.

20:20.719 --> 20:22.588 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What did Trump do today?

20:22.621 --> 20:27.259 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: Well, what
