60 days.

20:44.844 --> 20:50.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, again, another sign that
Trump wants to
fast-track this, because, as we
remember from

20:50.149 --> 20:58.691 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
