long time
and kind of became a symbol of
President Obama's

20:58.724 --> 21:04.130 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
environmental goals and it
really also galvanized
the environmentalists.

21:04.163 --> 21:08.701 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: So, these
orders don't guarantee
that they will go forward.

21:08.734 --> 21:11.871 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They just seemed to move the
ball much closer
to the goalposts, right?

21:11.904 --> 21:16.142 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: Right, but
this will be
-- you know, everything will be
at the discretion

21:16.175 --> 21:19.145 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
of the various agencies
involved.

21:19.178 --> 21:24.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I guess one could assume
that they would
lean in favor, because now we
have a different

21:24.150 --> 21:25.484 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
administration in.

21:25.518 --> 21:28.020 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We can also expect to see legal
challenges.

21:28.053 --> 21:33.125 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The lawyer for the Standing Rock
Tribe said
that they're going to be
focusing on the legal

21:33.159 --> 21:34.126 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
battles.

21:34.160 --> 21:35.928 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They are going to be in court.

21:35.961 --> 21:38.664 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: President
Trump has said
all along that this is about
jobs primarily.

21:38.697 --> 21:42.601 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Do we have a sense of how many
jobs these
two pipelines would generate?

21:42.635 --> 21:47.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: He said this
morning when
he was announcing these orders
that the Keystone

21:47.039 --> 21:50.309 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
