or two dozen
jobs.

21:57.883 --> 21:59.151 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Two dozen
jobs?

21:59.185 --> 22:00.553 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: Yes.

22:00.586 --> 22:03.856 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
