and the temporary

22:10.196 --> 22:11.964 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
jobs.

22:11.997 --> 22:15.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that environmental
groups will
argue that, as far as these
pipelines being

22:15.134 --> 22:21.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
job creators, in the long term,
