just much fewer

22:21.440 --> 22:23.709 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
than the temporary jobs.

22:23.742 --> 22:30.382 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we saw President Trump
yesterday met with
labor union representatives,
very strong proponents

22:30.416 --> 22:35.554 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of both these pipeline projects,
and they
were very, very happy after
their meeting

22:35.588 --> 22:38.457 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
with President Trump yesterday.

22:38.490 --> 22:43.862 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And one of the labor leaders
today said, you
know, we're really excited to
see, you know,

22:43.896 --> 22:45.431 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
he's not all talk, he's action.

22:45.464 --> 22:47.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And they were very happy to see
it early on.

22:47.700 --> 22:51.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: There were a
few other executive
orders that the president issued
today that

22:51.103 --> 22:52.338 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
also pertained to this.

22:52.371 --> 22:54.139 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What were these about?

22:54.173 --> 22:59.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: So, these
