projects.

23:04.250 --> 23:05.651 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: So, speeding
the process
along?

23:05.684 --> 23:07.419 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
VALERIE VOLCOVICI: Speeding the
process.

23:07.453 --> 23:14.860 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
