Hollywood musicals and...

43:49.360 --> 43:50.561 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Like such as?

43:50.595 --> 43:55.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: I like "Singin'
in the Rain,"
"Top Hat."

43:55.666 --> 44:04.742 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I think, as soon as I fell in
love with
those movies, I was thinking
already about,

44:04.775 --> 44:08.212 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
