that today?

44:08.246 --> 44:14.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: What did you hear
in those
films?

44:14.151 --> 44:16.320 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What grabbed you, at whatever
age you were?

44:16.354 --> 44:22.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: The reveling in
what only
movies can do, the sort of
unbridled experimentation,

44:22.827 --> 44:30.968 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the audacity, the privileging of
emotion over
anything else, the privileging
of image and

44:31.002 --> 44:36.541 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
sound and telling a story that
