the most liberating form for a
filmmaker.

44:48.352 --> 44:57.762 align:left position:37.5%,start line:80% size:62.5%
The
language of falling in love
through dance,

44:57.795 --> 45:01.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
especially in a movie like "Top
Hat" or a
movie like "Swing Time," a
number like, "Isn't

45:01.799 --> 45:05.770 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It a Lovely Day to Be Caught in
