45:13.611 --> 45:26.190 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the song and the dance is
what tells you,
oh, actually, there's something
underneath

45:26.223 --> 45:28.025 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

45:28.059 --> 45:38.202 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: You're also
working here with
actors Ryan Gosling and Emma
Stone, who are

45:38.235 --> 45:39.704 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
not known for singing and
dancing.

45:39.737 --> 45:41.472 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: Yes.

45:41.505 --> 45:44.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Part of the intention was to not
have it be
people who you had seen in a
musical before,

45:44.742 --> 45:47.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
so it's not a situation where
