of sitting there waiting for
them to break

45:47.244 --> 45:49.013 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
into song, you know?

45:49.046 --> 45:52.216 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I wanted to cast actors, first
