46:41.932 --> 46:47.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He first gained widespread
attention in 2014
with "Whiplash," about a young
drummer who

46:47.571 --> 46:53.244 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
