music?

47:16.300 --> 47:19.837 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: Well, you know,
that it's
not just about putting a camera
on someone

47:19.870 --> 47:23.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
