48:04.615 --> 48:05.750 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: Yes.

48:05.783 --> 48:07.551 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And I wonder what
