48:11.956 --> 48:12.923 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the wrong...

48:12.957 --> 48:14.692 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In the wrong era.

48:14.725 --> 48:18.596 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: The wrong era,
