bit, to try...

49:24.829 --> 49:25.996 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Scare you?

49:26.030 --> 49:27.832 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAMIEN CHAZELLE: Yes.

